  about 30 bugs; see WHATSNEW.txt.  Updated to samba-vscan-0.3.2.  Install
  libsmbclient.h #15357.  Added --with-winbind-auth-challenge #15748.  Add
  --with-winbind-ldap-hack if USE=ldap.  Re-org some stuff.

